on dynasty]]\n[[Category:1590s in Japan]]\n[[Category:Japan\u2013Korea relations]]\n", "name_user": "A", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Japanese_invasions_of_Korea_(1592%E2%80%931598)"}
